			"system": {
				"description": {
					"gm": "",
					"value": "<p>Illusions bend light around the target, rendering it @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.zJxUflt9np0q4yML]{Invisible}. This makes it @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.VRSef5y1LmL2Hkjf]{Undetected} to all creatures, though the creatures can attempt to find the target, making it @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.iU0fEDdBp3rXpTMC]{Hidden} to them instead. If the target uses a hostile action, the spell ends after that hostile action is completed.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Heightened (4th)</strong> The spell lasts 1 minute, but it doesn't end if the target uses a hostile action.</p>"
